  "detailed_description": "Hexes, a new puzzle game from Elektri.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMove gems across the game board to get matches of 3. But, watch out, moving a single gem will move all gems, and adds more gems to the board.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlan your moves carefully. Once the board is full of gems its game over. Matching 3 or more gems will remove them from the board and keep your game going.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWith lots of challenge and replay-ability, how high will your score in Hexes be?",
